413172935/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=052808_06 |date=April 13, 2010 }}</ref>\n! 5.3\n|-\n| Tuesday 8:30&nbsp;p.m.\n| April 15, 2008\n| May 27, 2008\n| 2007\u20132008\n! #171<ref name=\"abcmedianet1\"/>\n! 4.1\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | '''8th'''\n| Tuesday 9:00&nbsp;p.m.\n| December 2, 2008\n| December 30, 2008\n| 2008\u20132009\n! #104<ref name=\"abcmedianet2\">[http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=051909_05] {{webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100131044226/http://abcmedianet.com/web/dnr/dispDNR.aspx?id=051909_05 |date=January 31, 2010 }}</ref>\n! 5.6\n|-\n| Tuesday 9:30&nbsp;p.m.\n| December 2, 2008\n| December 30, 2008\n| 2008\u20132009\n! #127<ref name=\"abcmedianet2\"/>\n! 4.8\n|-\n| Tuesday 8:00&nbsp;p.m.\n| April 14, 2009\n| June 2, 2009\n| 2008\u20132009\n! #148<ref name=\"abcmedianet2\"/>\n! 3.8\n|-\n| Tuesday 8:30&nbsp;p.m.\n| April 14, 2009\n| June 2, 2009\n| 2008\u20132009\n! #149<ref name=\"abcmedianet2\"/>\n! 3.8\n|}\n\n===Accolades===\n{{Unreferenced|section|date=June 2019}}\n''According to Jim'' was nominated for 20 awards, including four [[Primetime Emmy Awards]] (all for cinematography).\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|+Awards and nominations\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Association\n! scope=\"col\"| Category\n! scope=\"col\"| Nominee\n! scope=\"col\"| Result\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2002\n|rowspan=2| [[Young Artist Awards]]\n|rowspan=2| Best Performance in a TV Series (Comedy or Drama) \u2013 Young Actress Age Ten or Under\n| Taylor Atelian\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Billi Bruno\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|2003\n| Young Artist Awards\n| Best Performance in a TV Series (Comedy or Drama) \u2013 Young Actress Age Ten or Under\n| Taylor Atelian\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2004\n|rowspan=2| Young Artist Awards\n|rowspan=2| Best Performance in a TV Series (Comedy or Drama) \u2013 Young Actress Age Ten or Under\n| Taylor Atelian\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Billi Bruno\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n|rowspan=2| 2005\n|rowspan=2| Youn