wn and Gus in Drag (Racing)\"; as Vanessa Minnillo\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[When I Was 17]]''\n| Herself\n| Episode 1.8; as Vanessa Minnillo\n|-\n| 2010 \n| ''This Little Piggy''\n|N/A\n| Television film; as Vanessa Minnillo\n|-\n| 2011\u20132012\n| ''[[Wipeout (2008 U.S. game show)|Wipeout]]''\n| Herself\n| also host; 24 episodes \n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[30 Rock]]''\n| Carmen Chao\n| Episode: \"\u00a1Qu\u00e9 Sorpresa!\"; as Vanessa Minnillo\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Hawaii Five-0 (2010 TV series)|Hawaii Five-0]]''\n| Susan\n| Episode: \"Powa Maka Moana\"; as Vanessa Minnillo\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''Nick & Vanessa's Dream Wedding''\n| Herself\n| Televised wedding (Reality television)\n|-\n| 2013\u20132014\n| ''[[Dads (2013 TV series)|Dads]]''\n| Camilla\n| Main role; 19 episodes \n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Lachey's: Raising the Bar]]''\n| Herself\n| Reality television\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Truth Be Told (U.S. comedy series)|Truth Be Told]]''\n| Tracy Cooper\n| Main role; 10 episodes\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''Sebastian Says''\n| Jenna \n| TV Movie\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[First Wives Club (TV series)]]'' (unaired pilot)\n| Sasha \n| Main role\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Dancing with the Stars (U.S. TV series)|Dancing with the Stars]]''\n| Herself / Contestant\n| [[Dancing with the Stars (U.S. season 25)|Season 25]]\n|-\n| 2017\u2013present\n| ''[[Top Chef Junior]]''\n| Host\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Miss USA 2018]]''\n| Co-Host\n| \n|-\n| 2018\n| ''A Twist of Christmas''\n| Abby Hewitt\n| TV Movie\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[American Housewife]]''\n| Crissy\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[Miss USA 2019]]''\n| Co-Host\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[BH90210]]''\n| \n| Guest role\n|-\n|2019\n| ''[[Love Is Blind (TV series)|Love Is Blind]]''\n|\n| Co-host\n|}\n\n===Music videos===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year !! Title !! Artist!! Role\n|-\n| 2006 || ''[[What's Left of Me (song)|What's Left of Me]]'' ||[[Nick Lachey]]|| Love Interest\n|}\n\n==See also==\n*[[Filipinos in the New York City metropolitan region]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|2}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.vanessalachey.com/ Official website]\n*{{IMDb name|591373|Vanessa Minnillo}}\n*{{People.com}}\n \n{{S-start}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Terrence J]] and [[Julianne Hough]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Host of [[Miss USA]] with [[Nick Lachey]]|years=[[Miss USA 2018|2018]], [[Miss USA 2019|2019]]}}\n{{s-inc}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Miss Teen USA titleholders}}\n{{South Carolina Pageant Winners}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lachey, Vanessa}}\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n[[Category:Actors from Charleston, South Carolina]]\n[[Category:Actresses from South Carolina]]\n[[Category:Actresses of Italian descent]]\n[[Category:American actresses of Filipino descent]]\n[[Category:American beauty pageant winners]]\n[[Category:American female models]]\n[[Category:American film actresses]]\n[[Category:American infotainers]]\n[[Category:American models of Filipino descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Irish descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Italian descent]]\n[[Category:American people of Kapampangan descent]]\n[[Category:American television hosts]]\n[[Category:American expatriates in Germany]]\n[[Category:American expatriates in Japan]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Military brats]]\n[[Category:Miss Teen USA 1998 delegates]]\n[[Category:Miss Teen USA winners]]\n[[Category:People from Angeles, Philippines]]\n[[Category:VJs (media personalities)]]\n[[Category:Women television presenters]]\n", "name_user": "Kbabej", "label": "safe", "comment": "Wording", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanessa_Lachey"}
